cu.explanation_en: Setting gNB_name to an empty string will cause name validation errors, leading to configuration rejection or system identification issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_name to an empty string will cause name validation errors, leading to configuration rejection or system identification issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_name 設定為空字串會導致名稱驗證錯誤，造成配置拒絕或系統識別問題。
